Author: adgonos.io
Title: [PRE-ICO LIVE][ANN] ADGONOS.IO - The $146 BILLION FUTURE of Mobile Economy
Body: Hi! We want to establish a mobile monetization framework that replaces conventional advertising methods. It would give developers more rewards while ensuring users an ad-free experience. Our coin would also facilitate in-app transactions. We hope that answers your question. Thanks for asking!

Author: adgonos.io
Title: [PRE-ICO LIVE][ANN] ADGONOS.IO - The $146 BILLION FUTURE of Mobile Economy
Body: Sure, allow us to explain in details.  First the PCs mine the ADG Coins using proof-of-work algorithms. Every one coin the PCs produce, an additional 0.25 coin is generated and put into a mobile 'reward pool'. Secondly, the developers implement our monetizing framework in their mobile apps, replacing the conventional advertising methods. (i.e. Google Ads) While the users download and use the said apps, their anonymous usage data would get collected, and sent directly to our servers. (Under the consent of the users, of course) The users would get rewarded with ADG coins, which can facilitate in-app purchases and transactions, while developers could also receive the coins for providing good content. The more the users use the app, the more coins they could receive, and the more the developers could earn income.  We hope to establish an entire mobile eco-system, and replace the current in-app purchase + monetization models.

Author: adgonos.io
Title: [PRE-ICO LIVE][ANN] ADGONOS.IO - The $146 BILLION FUTURE of Mobile Economy
Body: Hi! Please allow us to explain our business model.  There won't be any payments in need to get rid of the ads. Users would not receive ANY ADS and get ADG coins for free. In return, users would (under consent) generate anonymous usage data, which could be further utilized by developers who adopted our framework. I hope that explains our idea clearly!

Author: adgonos.io
Title: [PRE-ICO LIVE][ANN] ADGONOS.IO - The $146 BILLION FUTURE of Mobile Economy
Body: Thanks for asking!  Actually, there won't be 'unsold tokens', since tokens are minted only when Ethereum is sent to our contract address. As for advisors, we do have very experienced legal advisors and financial advisors to guide us through both fields. I hope that answers your question, and we expect to see you on board as one of the members of our ADGONOS family!

Author: adgonos.io
Title: [PRE-ICO LIVE][ANN] ADGONOS.IO - The $146 BILLION FUTURE of Mobile Economy
Body: Thanks for asking!  Here I'll provide explanation regarding our project as detailed as possible. There are basically three 'steps' in the whole process. 1. The computer miner mines ADG coins using Proof-of-Work, and generate 25% extra coins into the 'mobile reward pool'. 2. Developers implement our SDK in their apps, to replace the conventional ad framework (i.e. Google Ads) 3. While users use these apps, their anonymous usage data will get collected and sent to our server (under the users' consent, and secure protocols) As a reward of sharing their telemetry data, users would be rewarded with 20% of coins from the reward pool, in addition to getting rid of annoying ads. Developers will get a 79% from the 'reward pool' as a incentive to use our framework and a reward of providing good app content.  Basically the more time a user stays on an app, the more data he/she could generate, and the more we would reward both the user and the developer.  Hope that explains how our business model works!

Author: adgonos.io
Title: [PRE-ICO LIVE][ANN] ADGONOS.IO - The $146 BILLION FUTURE of Mobile Economy
Body: Regarding this part, we believe that although being a conglomerate that often plays monopoly, Google would possibly not outright ban an entire monetization framework. It allows apps adopting other ad frameworks (i.e. Unity ads) to be listed on the Play store as well. However, if in some extreme condition that really happens, we may encourage developers to switch to other stores to deploy to.  I hope that explains the question. Thanks for asking!

Author: adgonos.io
Title: [PRE-ICO LIVE][ANN] ADGONOS.IO - The $146 BILLION FUTURE of Mobile Economy
Body: Thanks for your comment! Actually, we are proposing a completely overhauled way of monetizing content. As stated on our website and in our whitepaper, the coins are first mined through PCs, and 25% extra coins would be generated into a 'reward pool'. Secondly, developers integrate our SDK into their apps, and replace the original monetizing framework (i.e. Google Ads) While users use their phones, their anonymous usage data would be generated and sent to our servers via a verifiable and open protocol to ensure the users' privacy. To reward the users for sharing their usage data, they would receive 20% ADG coins from the reward pool, in addition to the freedom of not having to view ads. The developers would then be rewarded with 79% of the coins from the 'reward pool' as reward for providing good app content. I hope that solves your confusion. As firm believers of privacy and a team who opposes monopoly and deceitful acts, we also dislike many companies' practice of throwing big words at us to grab attention. I hope you understand that isn't the case for us. You can view our website https://adgonos.io for more info!

Title: [PRE-ICO LIVE][ANN] ADGONOS.IO - The $146 BILLION FUTURE of Mobile Economy
Body: Thanks for keeping an eye on ADGONOS! We've been plotting and planning the ICO, including auditing the smart contract, writing the whitepaper, constructing the website, and think about possible caveats of our project, etc.  Yes, we do use KYC. However, we will conduct KYC after the crowd sale. It goes something like this: 1. You invest in ADGONOS, and register your Email and ERC 20 address 2. We will send the ADG Tokens to your ERC 20 wallet, but the tokens would be locked (i.e. you can't transfer to other addresses) 3. After 15 of July, we will send you the KYC form to the Email you registered in Step 1 4. After completing the KYC, we would unlock the ADG Tokens of all investors.  If you have any questions, feel free to contact us! Stay tuned to our social channels for more updates.

Author: adgonos.io
Title: [PRE-ICO LIVE][ANN] ADGONOS.IO - The $146 BILLION FUTURE of Mobile Economy
Body: WEBSITE | WHITEPAPER | TELEGRAM | TWITTER  Investing Tutorial Official Press Release Video!  ADGONOS.IO - Mobile Ads Gone, Forever. Website: https://adgonos.io/   PRESS  YAHOO!: "...ADGONOS Will Potentially Reshape the Mobile Economy Completely."  NewTalk.tw (LEADING INTERNET MEDIA OUTLET IN ASIA): "...a Truly Disruptive and Feasible Project."  Hinet.net (POPULAR INTERNET NEWS SOURCE IN TAIWAN): "Genuinely Innovative"  China Times (Taiwan)  Bepo TV (Taiwan)  Yiper News (China)  BitScreener Press Release    OUR STORY   Hi all. We are a group of students from major universities across Asia, including the University of Hong Kong (HKU), National Taiwan University, National Tsing Hua University, etc. We've stumbled upon numerous ICO projects since the boom of the cryptocurrency market in 2017, and even personally invested in quite a few. However, the more ICO projects we invested in, the more we realize that a feasible and prospective ICO may not always be the one that succeeds in funding. Frankly speaking, moreover, we've seen several ICOs with shallow ideas, coupled with vaporware, flashy promotional animation clips and buzzwords scamming the crowd, running away with millions, if not billions of dollars, all are forged with the investors' blood, sweat and tears. Besides costing the investors dearly, the circulation of scams even landed the whole crypto-market a bad fame. It is most evident with the fall of BitConnect, a ponzi-scheme making hundreds of thousands of investors bankrupt.  We want to change that.  Our founder, Kai-hsiang Chang, is a 19-year-old Taiwanese student studying at HKU. As a "coding junkie", he loves spending endless nights in front of a computer screen programming since the age of 14. He has aspired to devote his professional knowledge into something he's passionate about, and hopefully, in the meantime, making the world a better place. One day, together with his roommate, Yi-tim Hsiao, they come up with the idea of ADGONOS, hoping to change the glaring issues that the current mobile monetization business model has: High Commission, Low Revenue, Poor User Experience, and Shady Data Collection.  (We're watching you, Cambridge Analytica and ZUCC)  Admittedly, we do not possess the same financial caliber as many other ICO projects, e.g. buying a paid position on some of the demanding ICO listing websites, mass-advertising on social media, doing massive airdrops or even worse, spamming emails and forums with bots or cheap labors.  However, we do have the knowledge and proficiency to execute our project we do have highly skilled team members from various fields to achieve our goals. We do have a zealous passion of really establishing something beneficial to human beings. Heck, we even have the courage to launch an ICO during these sad times of bear market.  It's not just another aimless cash-grab to launder your cash, buy Lamborghinis or travel to some exotic Pacific islands. We truly want, and are capable of, building a product, that would last long, and reshape the traditional, outdated, and flawed business model of mobile ads. We just need your help, to make both our dreams, of improving the experience and revenue of app users and developers, and your dreams, of your crypto-portfolio mooning (well, with high probability  ), come true.     Hence, We Present to You, ADGONOS.IO    ADGONOS INTRODUCTION   ADGONOS  the first ICO launched by students from top-notch universities across Asia. The ADGONOS framework provides an ad-free environment for mobile app users, as well as increased revenue for app developers. Attractive to both app developers and app users, ADGONOS will significantly impact the current mobile ad market, of which annual turnover is 106 billion USD and annual growth rate is 18%. In the ADGONOS system, mobile app users and app developers are rewarded ADG coins, which are generated by Proof-of-Work (PoW) and anonymous usage data collection. The coins can be traded with other cryptocurrencies on exchanges or be spent as credit in in-app purchases.  There are three main roles in the ADGONOS system:  Miners: Mine and receive ADG using PoW algorithms on PC, generating an additional 25% of coins for users and developers.  App Users: Receive free ADG (can be spent in-app) from using apps (Proof of Usage), and generate anonymous data for the network.  App Developers: Adopt ADGONOS (instead of ads) in apps, and receive ADG as revenue while gathering in-depth analytic and usage data.  For illustrations, see the Imgur link below: https://i.imgur.com/D88oZak.png    ADGONOS ADVANTAGES   No ads, better user experience ADGONOS offers an ad-free environment for app users  Higher income for both app users and app developers RPKHU of app users: rises from 0 USD to 1.9032 USD** RPKHU of app developers: rises from 4.2144 USD to 7.5177 USD** (78% increase) *RPKHU: Revenue per kilo usage hour, index for measuring the revenue of apps **: Expected value based on the model, please refer to whitepaper for detailed information  97.5% decrease in commission fee Traditional ad agencies take away 40% from ad revenue. However, we only charge 1% commission fee to keep ADGONOS operational.  In-app purchase discount and zero transaction cost App users: enjoy price discount in in-app purchase App developers: gain 100% of revenue in in-app sales  Anonymous data collection with transparent policy App users: do not need to worry for shady data collection App developers: can acquire analytical data for app improvement    ICO DETAILS  Total Soft Cap: 2000 ETH Total Hard Cap: 40000 ETH Total issued tokens: 534,375,000 ADG Total tokens available for sale: 80% or 427,500,000 ADG: Currencies accepted: Ethereum (ETH)  Pre-ICO Phase: 00:00, 15 May 2018 (GMT +8) to 23:59, 28 May 2018 (GMT +8) Total tokens available: 62,500,000 ADG Hard cap: 5,000 ETH Minimum buying transaction: 0.5 ETH Bonus: 25% Price: 1 ETH = 12,500 ADG (bonus included)  ICO Phase I: 00:00, 1 June 2018 (GMT +8) to 23:59, 21 June 2018 (GMT +8) Total tokens available: 165,000,000 ADG Hard cap: 15,000 ETH Minimum buying transaction: 0.5 ETH Bonus: 10% Price: 1 ETH = 11,000 ADG (bonus included)  ICO Phase II: 00:00, 22 June 2018 (GMT +8) to 23:59, 15 July 2018 (GMT +8) Total tokens available: 200,000,000 ADG Hard cap: 20,000 ETH Minimum buying transaction: 0.5 ETH Price: 1 ETH = 10,000 ADG   TEAM MEMBERS  KAI-HSIANG CHANG Founder, CEO Studying Computer Science at the University of Hong Kong. A full stack developer who is keen on constantly exploring new territories. https://www.linkedin.com/in/kchaxcer    YI-TIM HSIAO Co-founder, CFO Studying Actuarial Science at the University of Hong Kong. Expert at analyzing statistical data and compiling definitive ramifications. https://www.linkedin.com/in/yi-tim-hsiao-048a6a15b    QI YAO SIAH Financial Advisor Studying Quantitative Finance at the University of Hong Kong. An experienced stock trader and analyst. https://www.linkedin.com/in/qiyaosiah    CHIH HUNG CHI Marketing Advisor Triple majoring in Physics, Statistic and Education at the University of Hong Kong. https://www.linkedin.com/in/chih-hung-chi-8462a1158  For the full list of members, check out our website's TEAM section https://adgonos.io    USEFUL INFO  Our Website: https://adgonos.io/ Whitepaper: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1AQU9714tGr9MhNFheAqyweCA4kIIMJo7/view Onepager (EN): https://drive.google.com/file/d/1rT2l8-3LogPuj0FCP39sldUVCI4RPGPN/view    SOCIAL LINKS  Telegram: https://t.me/adg_grp_en Facebook: https://facebook.com/adgonosio-896701057167539/ Twitter: https://twitter.com/adgonos_io Medium: https://medium.com/@adgonos.io E-mail: info@adgonos.io  For more detailed information, please refer to our website: https://adgonos.io/ Please feel free to contact us or give us advice!
